ase]] \u2013 guitar\n*[[Johnny Colt]] \u2013 bass\n*[[Steve Gorman]] \u2013 drums, percussion\n|\n*''[[Shake Your Money Maker (album)|Shake Your Money Maker]]'' (1990)\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"|November 1991 \u2013 August 1997\n|\n*Chris Robinson \u2013 lead vocals, harmonica\n*Rich Robinson \u2013 guitar, backing vocals\n*'''[[Marc Ford]] \u2013 guitar, backing vocals'''\n*Johnny Colt \u2013 bass\n*Steve Gorman \u2013 drums, percussion\n*'''[[Eddie Harsch]] \u2013 keyboards, piano'''<br />{{small|(initially a touring member 1991\u201392)}}\n|\n*''[[The Southern Harmony and Musical Companion|The Southern Harmony and<br />Musical Companion]]'' (1992)\n*''[[Amorica]]'' (1994)\n*''[[Three Snakes and One Charm]]'' (1996)\n*''[[Sho' Nuff Live]]'' (1998)\n*''[[The Lost Crowes]]'' (2006)\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"|August \u2013 October 1997\n|\n*Chris Robinson \u2013 lead vocals, harmonica\n*Rich Robinson \u2013 guitar, backing vocals\n*Johnny Colt \u2013 bass\n*Steve Gorman \u2013 drums, percussion\n*Eddie Harsch \u2013 keyboards, piano\n|none\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"|December 1997 \u2013 June 1998\n|\n*Chris Robinson \u2013 lead vocals, harmonica\n*Rich Robinson \u2013 guitar, backing vocals\n*'''[[Sven Pipien]] \u2013 bass, backing vocals'''\n*Steve Gorman \u2013 drums, percussion\n*Eddie Harsch \u2013 keyboards, piano\n|\n*''[[By Your Side (The Black Crowes album)|By Your Side]]'' (1999)\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"|June 1998 \u2013 May 2000\n|\n*Chris Robinson \u2013 lead vocals, harmonica\n*Rich Robinson \u2013 guitar, backing vocals\n*'''[[Audley Freed]] \u2013 guitar''' {{small|(touring only)}}\n*Sven Pipien \u2013 bass, backing vocals\n*Steve Gorman \u2013 drums, percussion\n*Eddie Harsch \u2013 keyboards, piano\n|\n*''[[Live at the Greek]]'' (2000)\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"|May \u2013 December 2000\n|\n*Chris Robinson \u2013 lead vocals, harmonica\n*Rich Robinson \u2013 guitar, backing vocals\n*Audley Freed \u2013 guitar\n*'''[[Greg Rzab]] \u2013 bass'''\n*Steve Gorman \u2013 drums, percussion\n